Text: This apparently is the 2005 film called "Good Night and Good Luck" starring George Clooney. Ted Cruz and the 2013 GOP do not appear in the film. The uploader is being quite misleading to suggest otherwise.
From the torrent title: "Good Night, Good Luck [2005]."  YES, so misleading!  And too, the IMDB link.  Darn, you caught me!  Troll.
